data.description: The perfect blend of accessibility and efficiency in this charming one-level home!  You will love the private wooded setting from this move-in ready home on acreage, but the real value is in its amazing location!  Just a short walk or drive to schools and public transit, or an easy commute to both Hwy 3 and 16.  This ADA-approved gem features spacious 36" hallways and a wheelchair-accessible shower, ensuring comfort and ease for all.  Save money with eco-friendly solar panels, the average electrical bill is just $8 a month for most of the year.  This home qualifies for VA financings, so buy for as low as $0 down, or assume the loan at 1.99% with a second mortgage or down payment.  This home should not be missed, arrange your showing today!
